## Features

- Data retention rules
- Privacy policies
- Security checklist
- Compliance reports

## Usage

```ts
import {
  complianceService,
  ComplianceChecker,
  ReportGenerator,
} from './src/compliance/index.js';

const checks = complianceService.runChecks();
const checker = new ComplianceChecker(complianceService);
checker.markPass(checks[0].id, 'policy reviewed');

const report = new ReportGenerator(complianceService).toMarkdown();
console.log(report);
```

